HEADWORD: Top billing
<hw>Top" bil*ling</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>the most
prominent place in an advertisement or program for a theatrical
performance, movie, fundraising affair, etc.; the place where the star's
name usually is located.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

